Out.

275
00:48:14.930 --> 00:48:19.230
It's... just us now.

276
00:48:20.100 --> 00:48:21.230
- See?
- Yes.

277
00:48:24.640 --> 00:48:26.000
Stop bullshitting me.

278
00:48:27.610 --> 00:48:30.510
Or else I'll throw you
in the fucking brig.

279
00:48:31.240 --> 00:48:35.080
If you know anything about me.
then go right ahead!

280
00:48:35.380 --> 00:48:36.450
Do whatever you want!

281
00:48:37.420 --> 00:48:40.350
But I don't have time for this.

282
00:48:42.520 --> 00:48:46.560
Hey. Easy. easy. Relax.

283
00:48:47.960 --> 00:48:51.200
Since you insist on being innocent...

284
00:48:52.100 --> 00:48:55.270
Okay. look at this.

285
00:48:57.300 --> 00:49:00.440
Do you recognize him? You know him?

286
00:49:05.640 --> 00:49:09.950
Let me refresh your memory with a story.

287
00:49:10.220 --> 00:49:12.250
This story might sound familiar to you.

288
00:49:25.960 --> 00:49:27.100
Ishmael.

289
00:49:31.470 --> 00:49:34.040
There was once a rumor...

290
00:49:35.470 --> 00:49:38.940
about a mysterious young man.

291
00:49:39.710 --> 00:49:41.180
Every time he appears.

292
00:49:42.110 --> 00:49:47.990
he leaves a scene of massacre
that turns the whole beach blood red.

293
00:49:49.020 --> 00:49:54.430
Children. none older than 6 or 10.
would disappear as well.

294
00:49:56.090 --> 00:49:59.100
Do you want to know
what happened to those children?

295
00:50:31.400 --> 00:50:36.070
<i>Those children grew up.</i>

296
00:50:37.670 --> 00:50:40.440
<i>They were bred to become smugglers...</i>

297
00:50:42.010 --> 00:50:43.210
<i>plunderers...</i>

298
00:50:44.510 --> 00:50:45.680
<i>and killers.</i>

299
00:50:49.210 --> 00:50:50.380
<i>Imagine that.</i>

300
00:50:51.620 --> 00:50:56.660
<i>These brats have a stranglehold</i>
<i>on this island.</i>

301
00:51:01.430 --> 00:51:02.790
<i>Sons of bitches.</i>

302
00:51:05.100 --> 00:51:08.670
<i>Everyone of them willing to die...</i>

303
00:51:09.570 --> 00:51:13.570
<i>for their mysterious</i>

304
00:51:13.640 --> 00:51:16.140
<i>terrorist master.</i>

305
00:51:17.610 --> 00:51:19.510
<i>Now. one has to wonder.</i>

306
00:51:20.510 --> 00:51:23.350
<i>Who is this person?</i>

307
00:51:25.250 --> 00:51:30.590
<i>Even amongst criminals.</i>
<i>he's a terrifying figure.</i>

308
00:51:32.220 --> 00:51:36.760
<i>Few who live to tell the tale...</i>

309
00:51:37.530 --> 00:51:41.570
<i>refer to him simply as "Lee."</i>

310
00:51:45.570 --> 00:51:48.210
What's it got to do with me?

311
00:51:49.210 --> 00:51:50.580
Two months ago...

312
00:51:52.410 --> 00:51:55.080
we hit the jackpot.

313
00:51:55.610 --> 00:52:00.420
<i>Right out of the blue.</i>

314
00:52:00.690 --> 00:52:02.550
<i>we found Lee.</i>

315
00:52:03.190 --> 00:52:07.290
<i>sitting out in the open.</i>

316
00:52:08.490 --> 00:52:11.800
<i>Unarmed. Unguarded.</i>

317
00:52:13.400 --> 00:52:14.800
<i>Imagine that.</i>

318
00:52:36.420 --> 00:52:37.420
<i>Crazy.</i>

319
00:52:41.560 --> 00:52:45.400
But you see. Ishmael.

320
00:52:46.160 --> 00:52:50.440
- It gets even crazier...
- You haven't answered my question.

321
00:53:04.880 --> 00:53:06.850
What do you say now. scum?

322
00:53:09.450 --> 00:53:13.460
Listen. I really don't know...

323
00:53:18.160 --> 00:53:19.630
Turn the lights back on!

324
00:53:41.690 --> 00:53:43.560
What the fuck is going on?

325
00:54:54.830 --> 00:54:55.830
Who are you?

326
00:54:56.930 --> 00:54:58.030
I am...

327
00:56:39.730 --> 00:56:40.730
Come on. let's go.

328
00:57:52.570 --> 00:57:53.770
Turn the power back on.

329
00:58:07.690 --> 00:58:09.020
Abdi...

330
00:59:59.130 --> 01:00:00.130
Three.

331
01:00:02.000 --> 01:00:02.870
Four.

332
01:01:33.320 --> 01:01:35.130
Hiding? Where the fuck are you?

333
01:01:36.430 --> 01:01:37.830
I still wanna play.

334
01:01:47.870 --> 01:01:50.240
Fuck. Not bad...

335
01:05:29.390 --> 01:05:30.560
Bro.

336
01:05:32.930 --> 01:05:33.900
Hey. bro.

337
01:05:40.610 --> 01:05:45.010
Wanna know what I did
to that bitch of yours?

338
01:05:48.580 --> 01:05:49.650
Fuck you!

339
01:06:59.680 --> 01:07:02.120
So. you're the one? Abdi's savior.

340
01:07:03.750 --> 01:07:05.420
What is he to you?

341
01:07:07.020 --> 01:07:09.660
A good name. Abdi.

342
01:07:11.330 --> 01:07:13.660
It's supposed to mean loyalty.

343
01:07:18.240 --> 01:07:19.370
Who are you?

344
01:08:22.370 --> 01:08:23.700
<i>Don't kill him.</i>

345
01:08:24.300 --> 01:08:27.240
Tell him we got his woman.

346
01:08:29.610 --> 01:08:30.580
Tejo?

347
01:08:31.810 --> 01:08:33.180
<i>I'm still here.</i>

348
01:08:34.650 --> 01:08:35.780
And I'll be coming.

349
01:08:47.290 --> 01:08:50.290
You still remember your father.
right. Abdi?

350
01:08:55.200 --> 01:08:56.200
Lee.

351
01:08:58.840 --> 01:09:00.140
That's my boy.

352
01:09:04.410 --> 01:09:05.440
<i>Ailin!</i>

353
01:09:09.650 --> 01:09:11.120
- <i>Ishmael.</i>
- Ailin!

354
01:09:11.750 --> 01:09:14.890
- <i>Lee! Let her go!</i>
- You hear that?

355
01:09:54.230 --> 01:09:55.660
You should've stabbed here.

356
01:09:57.500 --> 01:10:00.200
I thought you were a doctor.

357
01:14:08.050 --> 01:14:09.410
Do you remember it now?

358
01:14:10.180 --> 01:14:12.120
All the memories from
that fucking place?

359
01:14:15.890 --> 01:14:18.920
You remember. right?
He threw us into that well.

360
01:14:20.720 --> 01:14:24.160
It's what separates him
from other scum.

361
01:14:25.560 --> 01:14:27.530
He took us from our parents.

362
01:14:28.570 --> 01:14:31.000
He taught us how to survive
and how to kill.

363
01:14:31.070 --> 01:14:36.540
<i>Days. even weeks. without food.</i>
<i>Without water.</i>

364
01:14:39.210 --> 01:14:42.510
Yet... it's that very suffering
that turned us into brothers.

365
01:15:02.070 --> 01:15:03.900
That's not how it ends though.

366
01:15:06.740 --> 01:15:07.600
Yeah.

367
01:15:08.570 --> 01:15:11.880
<i>A bottle of water could turn</i>
<i>desperate kids into murderers.</i>

368
01:15:21.050 --> 01:15:24.120
<i>Hence. the father from hell.</i>

369
01:15:26.190 --> 01:15:29.260
If you know all about it.
why are you still on his side?

370
01:15:29.530 --> 01:15:33.730
Everyone has to choose a side.
Following that fucker is my fate.

371
01:15:35.270 --> 01:15:39.170
You have a new lease on life.
Why are you here?

372
01:15:40.140 --> 01:15:42.510
Back off and I'll let you live.

373
01:15:42.970 --> 01:15:43.840
Besi...

374
01:15:45.840 --> 01:15:47.080
I can't back off now.

375
01:15:48.850 --> 01:15:49.850
All this for the doctor?

376
01:15:52.950 --> 01:15:55.620
Like you said.
everyone has to choose a side.

377
01:16:02.060 --> 01:16:04.190
This won't be as easy as Tejo or Tano.

378
01:19:05.440 --> 01:19:06.740
Well done. Abdi.

379
01:19:08.110 --> 01:19:09.380
Now comes the final drill.

380
01:20:03.330 --> 01:20:04.270
Abdi...

381
01:21:28.290 --> 01:21:30.090
Besi was always on your side.

382
01:21:30.590 --> 01:21:32.090
And this is how you repay him?

383
01:21:37.190 --> 01:21:39.200
You're tearing us apart. Abdi!

384
01:22:06.590 --> 01:22:08.490
Remember me. Abdi?

385
01:22:21.410 --> 01:22:23.640
Or should I call you Ishmael?

386
01:22:25.240 --> 01:22:26.380
Where's Ailin?

387
01:22:27.980 --> 01:22:29.110
Take me to her.

388
01:22:38.490 --> 01:22:40.560
I don't know which makes me sadder.

389
01:22:41.320 --> 01:22:44.090
watching you killing your own...

390
01:22:47.430 --> 01:22:49.330
or seeing the sorry state you're in now.

391
01:22:52.400 --> 01:22:54.200
Do you know how close we were?

392
01:22:59.480 --> 01:23:01.310
Why does it have to change. Abdi?

393
01:23:05.720 --> 01:23:08.290
Probably because you put
a bullet in my head.

394
01:23:13.520 --> 01:23:15.260
You betrayed father. right?

395
01:23:16.960 --> 01:23:18.600
If you ask me to choose...

396
01:23:21.230 --> 01:23:23.100
you know whom I would choose.

397
01:23:24.430 --> 01:23:25.470
Rika...

398
01:23:26.970 --> 01:23:31.240
this has been going for far too long.
I don't wanna kill anymore.

399
01:23:36.050 --> 01:23:38.620
So. it's all about her. right?

400
01:23:38.680 --> 01:23:40.420
Leave Ailin out of this.

401
01:23:53.730 --> 01:23:55.770
Since you want her that bad...

402
01:23:56.630 --> 01:23:57.600
Rika!

403
01:24:09.350 --> 01:24:10.280
Rika.

404
01:25:47.440 --> 01:25:48.510
That's enough. Rika.

405
01:27:11.260 --> 01:27:11.930
Rika.

406
01:27:14.500 --> 01:27:15.500
That's enough.

407
01:27:41.930 --> 01:27:45.500
Remember this place?
We trained here as kids.

408
01:27:49.630 --> 01:27:52.240
Even then. I always admired you. Abdi.

409
01:27:54.440 --> 01:27:56.470
Those were the happiest moments.

410
01:27:57.310 --> 01:27:58.410
Listen to me.

411
01:27:59.880 --> 01:28:01.640
You can get away from Lee.

412
01:28:04.450 --> 01:28:05.950
You have the choice to be free.

413
01:28:24.830 --> 01:28:25.800
Rika.

414
01:29:22.490 --> 01:29:23.760
Rika. no...

415
01:29:28.930 --> 01:29:30.030
Now...

416
01:29:31.600 --> 01:29:33.500
we're even.

417
01:29:41.080 --> 01:29:42.050
Rika.

418
01:30:38.570 --> 01:30:39.770
<i>I remember everything.</i>

419
01:30:41.140 --> 01:30:43.140
<i>You raised us to be wolves.</i>

420
01:30:45.510 --> 01:30:47.110
<i>All we were good for was killing.</i>

421
01:30:49.880 --> 01:30:52.620
<i>It was meant to make you all stronger.</i>

422
01:30:53.480 --> 01:30:54.550
Maybe so.

423
01:30:55.020 --> 01:30:56.550
But it's all apparent now.

424
01:30:57.190 --> 01:30:59.760
You're neither a legend. nor a father.

425
01:31:01.920 --> 01:31:02.890
FREE OR DIE

426
01:31:02.960 --> 01:31:05.160
Just an old man who bullies little kids.

427
01:31:07.060 --> 01:31:08.700
In the end you made a mistake.

428
01:31:10.900 --> 01:31:11.900
Okay.

429
01:31:12.800 --> 01:31:14.940
Why don't you just come home.

430
01:31:16.110 --> 01:31:17.570
We'll settle this.

431
01:31:18.940 --> 01:31:20.080
<i>I'm already here.</i>

432
01:31:30.590 --> 01:31:32.760
Hurry! Hurry!

433
01:31:36.660 --> 01:31:38.230
Go hide in the corner.

434
01:31:40.660 --> 01:31:42.470
Where's the key?

435
01:31:53.840 --> 01:31:54.880
Get up.

436
01:31:56.250 --> 01:31:57.680
Come on. get up.

437
01:31:59.250 --> 01:32:00.120
Turn around.

438
01:32:00.850 --> 01:32:02.850
- Why?
- I said. turn around!

439
01:32:27.080 --> 01:32:27.940
Stay still!

440
01:32:54.970 --> 01:32:56.140
Fucking bitch!

441
01:33:33.110 --> 01:33:34.740
You're both dead!

442
01:33:48.930 --> 01:33:51.290
Bitch! You can't even shoot.

443
01:33:55.800 --> 01:33:57.130
No. wait! Drop it!

444
01:34:18.920 --> 01:34:20.120
Let's get the hell out.

445
01:34:34.200 --> 01:34:36.640
Let's go. Let's go.

446
01:34:59.660 --> 01:35:00.830
This way.

447
01:35:39.240 --> 01:35:40.300
What was that?

448
01:36:05.330 --> 01:36:06.400
Ailin.

449
01:36:08.030 --> 01:36:09.130
It's me.

450
01:36:23.780 --> 01:36:24.810
Ailin?

451
01:36:29.090 --> 01:36:30.420
Ailin. are you all right?

452
01:36:34.920 --> 01:36:35.960
Ailin...

453
01:36:38.330 --> 01:36:40.060
I'm so sorry.

454
01:36:45.070 --> 01:36:46.440
- Are you hurt bad?
- Shut up!

455
01:36:51.870 --> 01:36:53.910
Ailin. please calm down.

456
01:36:55.440 --> 01:36:59.020
Get out of the way! We're leaving.

457
01:37:00.350 --> 01:37:01.880
Yes. we will leave.

458
01:37:07.090 --> 01:37:08.560
You're one of them.

459
01:37:13.930 --> 01:37:15.530
You are exactly like them!

460
01:37:19.800 --> 01:37:20.570
Yes.

461
01:37:22.970 --> 01:37:24.040
You're right.

462
01:37:26.580 --> 01:37:29.410
Everything that I've done
to get away from them...

463
01:37:32.210 --> 01:37:35.320
brought me to this day.
this very second.

464
01:37:45.590 --> 01:37:47.330
You saved me before.

465
01:37:51.070 --> 01:37:54.940
I need you to save me one more time.

466
01:38:17.490 --> 01:38:18.530
Ishmael...

467
01:38:55.100 --> 01:38:56.500
Wake up! Wake up!

468
01:39:29.270 --> 01:39:32.400
Why are you looking over there?
Look at me.

469
01:39:34.440 --> 01:39:36.010
I said. look at me!

470
01:39:36.540 --> 01:39:38.210
I'm your father!

471
01:39:43.250 --> 01:39:44.350
You...

472
01:39:45.450 --> 01:39:50.390
are just a fucking dog
that doesn't know the word "obey."

473
01:39:57.630 --> 01:39:58.690
Where's Rika?

474
01:40:05.370 --> 01:40:06.440
Is she dead?

475
01:40:10.210 --> 01:40:11.270
You killed her?

476
01:40:22.180 --> 01:40:23.550
She died a long time ago.

477
01:40:25.290 --> 01:40:27.460
From the moment
you pulled her out of that well.

478
01:40:28.490 --> 01:40:31.160
All of them died
when you first laid your hands on them.

479
01:40:33.560 --> 01:40:36.600
Why? Why all this? What for?!

480
01:40:37.530 --> 01:40:41.170
You're my son. Abdi! My son!

481
01:40:42.240 --> 01:40:43.240
Abdi?

482
01:40:50.280 --> 01:40:53.420
For every time you call
me by that name...

483
01:41:11.400 --> 01:41:12.670
So be it. then.

484
01:44:05.370 --> 01:44:06.440
My son...

485
01:44:09.710 --> 01:44:10.650
you know...

486
01:44:11.310 --> 01:44:14.880
raising you was my greatest mistake...

487
01:44:16.220 --> 01:44:18.790
and I have to pay for it.

488
01:44:24.890 --> 01:44:27.300
And so will you...

489
01:44:28.930 --> 01:44:30.000
Abdi.

490
01:46:17.370 --> 01:46:18.410
Lee!

491
01:49:00.600 --> 01:49:01.600
Ishmael.

492
01:49:02.870 --> 01:49:03.870
Ishmael.

493
01:49:04.570 --> 01:49:05.610
Ishmael.

494
01:49:06.010 --> 01:49:07.640
Don't close your eyes. Ishmael.

495
01:49:12.680 --> 01:49:14.720
Ishmael. Just look at me.

496
01:49:16.590 --> 01:49:18.290
Ishmael. Ishmael.

497
01:49:23.890 --> 01:49:25.660
Don't leave me.

498
01:49:36.240 --> 01:49:39.140
Please... Ishmael.

499
01:52:03.020 --> 01:52:04.750
This feels familiar.

500
01:52:06.420 --> 01:52:07.960
So. how's Jakarta?

501
01:52:13.430 --> 01:52:15.360
At least the bed's better this time.

502
01:52:22.240 --> 01:52:24.740
Just wait until you get out.

503
01:52:28.980 --> 01:52:30.710
You've experienced nothing yet.

504
01:52:34.080 --> 01:52:35.320
So. please...

505
01:52:39.150 --> 01:52:41.720
Don't make me wait
another two months this time.

506
01:52:43.890 --> 01:52:44.890
Okay?

507
01:52:46.330 --> 01:52:47.330
Okay?

508
01:53:29.470 --> 01:53:31.540
PATIENT DIAGNOSIS

509
01:53:36.510 --> 01:53:40.280
NAME:

510
01:54:18.850 --> 01:54:20.090
You should write...

511
01:54:23.590 --> 01:54:25.030
Ishmael.

511
01:54:26.305 --> 01:55:26.570
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-
